snippet: McIlroy secured his second Dubai Desert Classic title in six years with a two-under-par 70 in the final round to win by three strokes in the United Arab Emirates on Sunday.
abstract: Rory McIlroy wins golf's Dubai Desert Classic.
lead_paragraph: McIlroy secured his second Dubai Desert Classic title in six years with a two-under-par 70 in the final round to win by three strokes in the United Arab Emirates on Sunday.

headline.main: Rory McIlroy Wins Second Dubai Title
